programme.title: Return Of The One-Armed...
programme.desc: One-armed Swordsman Fang Kang wants to lead a quiet life with his wife, but when she is abducted by the Eight Demon Swordsmen clan, he is forced to take them on in order to save her.

programme.title: Return Of The One-Armed...
programme.desc: Pendekar pedang satu tangan Fang Kang ingin menjalani kehidupan yang tenang bersama istrinya, tapi saat istrinya diculik oleh klan Pendekar Delapan Pedang Iblis, ia terpaksa melawan mereka demi menyelamatkannya.

programme.title: Tropicana Interlude
programme.desc: Ping and Su are lovers who operate a travel agency specializing in Southeast Asian holidays. Tung, a school mistress, and her students join a guided tour lead by Ping.

programme.title: Tropicana Interlude
programme.desc: Ping dan Su adalah sepasang kekasih yang mengelola agen perjalanan khusus liburan ke Asia Tenggara. Seorang kepala sekolah bernama Tung beserta murid-muridnya bergabung dalam tur yang dipimpin oleh Ping.

programme.title: The King Boxer
programme.desc: A rich boy obsessed with martial arts encounters a mysterious man who teaches him combat skills, allowing him to win in a duel and marry his love.

programme.title: The King Boxer
programme.desc: Seorang bocah kaya yang terobsesi dengan seni bela diri bertemu pria misterius yang mengajarinya keterampilan bertarung, sehingga ia bisa memenangkan sebuah duel dan menikahi sang pujaan hati.

programme.title: The Scandalous Warlord
programme.desc: General Feng occupies the city of Shandong, and soldiers and civilians alike welcome him without knowing his tyrannical and lustful nature.

programme.title: The Scandalous Warlord
programme.desc: Jenderal Feng menguasai kota Shandong. Tentara dan warga sipil di sana menyambutnya tanpa mengetahui sifat kejam dan nafsunya yang menyeramkan.

programme.title: The Sword Of Swords
programme.desc: A noble swordsman fights to recover the magical blade that has protected his country for centuries after being blinded and betrayed by a ruthless villain. A cunning killer has blinded the brave warrior chosen to defend his country with an enchanted sword, and murdered his family.

programme.title: The Monkey Goes West
programme.desc: Another film inspired by the Chinese classic tale Journey to the West. This memorable version presents a unique interpretation with humour, action, and fantasy galore.

programme.title: The Monkey Goes West
programme.desc: Film mengesankan yang diangkat dari kisah klasik Perjalanan Ke Barat ini menampilkan interpretasi nan unik yang dibumbui dengan humor, aksi laga dan kisah fantasi.

programme.title: 7-Man Army
programme.desc: In 1933, 20,000 Japanese soldiers and 50 tanks strategically invaded the Great Wall.

programme.title: 7-Man Army
programme.desc: Pada tahun 1933, 20.000 tentara dan 50 tank Jepang menyerbu Tembok Besar Tiongkok.

programme.title: The Mad Monk Strikes Again
programme.desc: The Mad Monk is up against the equally legendary scholar-turned-genie, Lu Tung Pin. The duo create havoc as they vie with each other, be it in mirth, magic, women or weapons!

programme.title: The Mad Monk Strikes Again
programme.desc: Seorang biksu gila menghadapi cendekiawan legendaris yang berubah menjadi jin, Lu Tung Pin. Keduanya menyebabkan kekacauan saat bersaing satu sama lain, baik dalam kesenangan, sihir, wanita, atau senjata!

programme.title: The Naval Commandos
programme.desc: The Chinese Navy is attempting to defend its coastline from a Japanese attack, they send their commando unit led by Cui Hsia into the mainland to enlist help to thwart the Japanese before they attack.

programme.title: A Place To Call Home
programme.desc: When she discovers she is adopted, Li Ching sets out in search of her real family, and things to go from bad to worse until she finally realizes that there's no place like home.

programme.title: A Place To Call Home
programme.desc: Saat mengetahui jika dirinya adalah anak adopsi, Li Ching pergi untuk mencari keluarganya. Ketika situasi yang dialaminya menjadi semakin memburuk, ia akhirnya menyadari bahwa rumah adalah tempat yang terbaik.

programme.title: Swordswomen Three
programme.desc: Three decades earlier, Shen Yi, Essie Lin Chia, and Pan Ying-tzu took on Shaw's first international superstar, Lo Lieh for the Han Family Sword, making this a four-star treat for action fans.

programme.title: Swordswomen Three
programme.desc: Pada awal tiga dekade, Shen Yi, Essie Lin Chia, dan Pan Ying-tzu menampilkan superstar internasional Shaw yang pertama, Lo Lieh untuk Han Family Sword memberikan suguhan bintang empat untuk penggemar film laga ini.

programme.title: The Pure And The Evil
programme.desc: What began as the sweet reunion of two high school friends quickly deteriorates into a deranged erotic nightmare when Rose takes a shine to former classmate Fang and her new fiance!

programme.title: The Pure And The Evil
programme.desc: Reuni dua teman SMA yang semula manis segera berubah menjadi mimpi buruk erotis yang mengerikan ketika Rose tertarik pada mantan teman sekelasnya, Fang, dan tunangan barunya!

programme.title: The Blood Brothers
programme.desc: Assassin Chang and his brother Hung meet up with a soldier, Mu. Together, they form a small mountain army, but when Hung's wife arrives, emotions swell, and Mu leaves for the army. After long, Mu summons his friends to join him, but all the while, he has longed for Hung's wife, and tries to have Hung murdered. This treason forces Hung to take up arms against his former comrade.

programme.title: Fast Fingers
programme.desc: After his release from prison, Uncle Bill returns to make a fortune with his past thieving partners. They continue to prey on the unsuspecting public, but are closely watched by the upright police chief.

programme.title: Fast Fingers
programme.desc: Setelah dibebaskan dari penjara, Paman Bill kembali untuk mendapatkan banyak uang bersama teman pencuri lamanya. Mereka mengincar warga biasa, tapi ternyata mereka diawasi dengan ketat oleh seorang kepala polisi.

programme.title: Shaolin Rescuers
programme.desc: Hong Xi Guan of Shaolin is chased and wounded by a martial arts scum who took refuge in the Qing court. He is saved and healed by friends from the wet market and they hide Hong in a bean curd shop to protect him.

programme.title: Shaolin Rescuers
programme.desc: Hong Xi Guan of Shaolin is chased and wounded by a martial arts scum who took refuge in the Qing court. He is saved and healed by friends from the wet market and they hide Hong in a bean curd shop to protect him.

programme.title: Summer Heat
programme.desc: The heavenly Jenny Hu plays the seductive Judy, who juggles three different men: a rich husband, a sexy playboy and sensitive intellectual, in her search for money, sex and love.

programme.title: Summer Heat
programme.desc: Si cantik Jenny Hu berperan sebagai Judy, sang penggoda yang merayu tiga pria berbeda: seorang pria kaya, seorang playboy seksi, dan seorang pria terpelajar nan sensitif dalam pencariannya akan uang, seks dan cinta.

programme.title: Brotherhood
programme.desc: Liu tries to live a respectable life and serve as a loyal member of his triad society. But over time his good intentions lead him into an all-out gang war with a startling conclusion.

programme.title: Brotherhood
programme.desc: Liu berupaya hidup terhormat dan mengabdi sebagai seorang anggota triad yang setia. Namun seiring berjalannya waktu, niat baik Liu membawanya ke dalam perang antargeng tanpa henti dengan dampak yang mengerikan.

programme.title: The Butterfly Chalice
programme.desc: Action maestro Chang Cheh tells the story of Chin Feng, who meets the beautiful Ting Hung while on the run for accidentally killing an arrogant bully.

programme.title: The Butterfly Chalice
programme.desc: Ahli film laga Chang Cheh menceritakan kisah tentang Chin Feng yang bertemu dengan gadis cantik bernama Ting Hung saat tengah melarikan diri, setelah ia tak sengaja membunuh seorang pengganggu yang sombong.

programme.title: The Spiritual Boxer
programme.desc: A con artist uses Kung Fu to swindle villagers for money by pretending to be possessed by angry gods. However, when the villagers are later threatened by bandits he must use the same skills for good.

programme.title: Love With The Perfect Stranger
programme.desc: After breaking up with his girlfriend, salesman Bao meets a rich girl, Jin Jin, who just broke up with her boyfriend. Two equally heartbroken strangers fall in love instantly and get married on impulse.

programme.title: Love With The Perfect Stranger
programme.desc: Setelah putus dengan pacarnya, seorang wiraniaga Bao bertemu dengan seorang gadis kaya, Jin Jin, yang juga baru putus dengan kekasihnya. Dua orang asing yang patah hati ini pun langsung jatuh cinta dan menikah.

programme.title: Five Tough Guys
programme.desc: A titular gang of misfits come together to protect a patriotic general from a scheming usurper. To this end, the unlikely heroes act as the general's escorts on a dangerous journey to a distant British consulate.

programme.title: Five Tough Guys
programme.desc: Sekelompok orang nan kikuk berkumpul untuk melindungi seorang jenderal patriotik dari orang yang berencana merebut kekuasaan. Mereka menjadi pengawalnya dalam perjalanan berbahaya ke konsulat Inggris.

programme.title: Forever Diamonds
programme.desc: Hua, a pretty fraud, steals a brilliant diamond ring from a shop in Hong Kong and escapes to Singapore. To smuggle the ring pass customs, Hua slips it into the pocket of a stranger, Yen, but then lost track of him.

programme.title: Forever Diamonds
programme.desc: Penipu cantik bernama Hua mencuri sebuah cincin berlian dari toko di Hong Kong dan kabur ke Singapura. Untuk menghindari bea cukai, ia memasukkan cincin itu ke dalam saku pria asing, tapi ia kehilangan jejaknya.

programme.title: The Black Butterfly
programme.desc: Black Butterfly, steals from the rich and gives to the poor. In reality, she is Bao Zhu, the daughter of retired swordsman Kwan Yee. Trouble starts when a bandit gang who she has robbed come to town looking for her.

programme.title: Sex, Love And Hate
programme.desc: In Sex, Love And Hate, director of erotica and kung-fu films Chu Yuan combines stars from both genres to create a masterpiece about Hong Kong society's differing views on love and what women want from it.

programme.title: Sex, Love And Hate
programme.desc: Dalam Sex, Love, And Hate, Chu Yuan menggabungkan bintang dari genre film kungfu dan film dewasa untuk mengangkat perbedaan pandangan masyarakat Hong Kong tentang cinta dan apa yang diinginkan wanita dari cinta.

programme.title: The Trail Of The Broken Blade
programme.desc: A young aristocratic knight Li Yueh renounces his sword, identity and the woman he loves after going on the lam for assassinating a corrupt official responsible for his father's demise.

programme.title: The Trail Of The Broken Blade
YUM Investigation
programme.desc: Yum, a detective agency that handles supernatural cases, investigates the evil spirits appearing in an old building. They discover that the spirits are created so that the building can be vacated for redevelopment.

programme.title: YUM Investigation
programme.desc: Sebuah kantor detektif yang menangani kasus supranatural, Yum, menyelidiki sejumlah roh jahat di suatu bangunan tua dan mendapati bahwa roh-roh itu diciptakan guna mengosongkan bangunan agar dapat dibangun kembali.

programme.title: Flashover
programme.desc: This is based on a true story. A sudden earthquake hits the gas pipes in an industrial park, triggering massive explosions and engulfing the neighboring area in flames. When the Fire Rescue Force reaches the scene, firefighters must fight against the flames and time, as they commit to safeguard lives with their own.

programme.title: Romantic Dream

programme.title: The White Storm 3: Heaven Or...
programme.desc: An undercover cop who invade a drug cartel led by a notorious Thai drug lord. In classic heroic bloodshed fashion, the two develop a bond of brotherhood.

programme.title: Two Tigers

programme.title: Two Tigers

programme.title: Mission Milano
programme.desc: A wealthy entrepreneur goes undercover with an Interpol agent to protect a new invention, the Seed of God, from falling into an international crime conglomerate.

programme.title: Echoes Of The Rainbow
programme.desc: Set in Hong Kong in the 1960s, the story revolves around the family of a hardworking shoemaker Mr Law, with his happy-go-lucky wife and two sons – a talented elder son and an eight-year-old eccentric younger son. While their lives are not always smooth-sailing, the family sticks together and support one another through thick and thin.

programme.title: Endless Battle
programme.desc: This is a story about two brothers. Both are involved in a drug cartel¿s turf battle and during an escort mission, Zhong discovers his brother¿s hidden identity. This leads to an endless battle between good and evil.

programme.title: Endless Battle
programme.desc: Sepasang kakak beradik terlibat dalam perebutan wilayah kartel narkoba. Saat menjalankan misi pengawalan, sang kakak menemukan identitas rahasia adiknya hingga memunculkan persaingan antara kebaikan dan kejahatan.

programme.title: Knockout
programme.desc: A former boxing champion and convict who has just been released from prison discovers that his wife has died and he is now a single parent. The situation is made worse with his daughter's diagnosis of leukaemia.

programme.title: Knockout
programme.desc: Seorang mantan juara tinju dan narapidana yang baru saja dibebaskan menyadari bahwa istrinya telah meninggal dan ia sekarang adalah orang tua tunggal. Situasinya menjadi lebih buruk dengan diagnosis leukemia putrinya.

programme.title: Tales From Occult: Body & Soul
programme.desc: This horror anthology series returns to feature three spooky crime stories about an ex-hair model, a cat lover and the love triangle between a dental nurse, a dentist and a chef.

programme.title: Tales From Occult: Body & Soul
programme.desc: Serial antologi horor ini kembali menampilkan tiga kisah kriminal nan menyeramkan tentang seorang mantan model rambut, pencinta kucing, dan cinta segitiga antara seorang perawat gigi, dokter gigi, dan koki.

programme.title: Rob N Roll
programme.desc: Decadent Murong Hui teams up with violent bandits after a botched robbery. A female detective pursues them as they scheme to steal a bag of money, leading to chaotic events due to betrayals and twists under the "I rob, you rob me" code.

programme.title: Rob N Roll
programme.desc: Murong Hui yang sudah tua bekerja sama dengan para bandit kejam setelah sebuah perampokan yang gagal. Sementara, seorang detektif wanita mengejar mereka saat mereka merencanakan pencarian sekantong uang, yang mengarah ke peristiwa kacau karena pengkhianatan dan tipu daya di bawah kode "I rob, you rob me".

programme.title: Lifeline
programme.desc: The story revolves around a dutiful yet indifferent fireman, who can march into disaster and risk his lives by saving others, yet would he have the equivalent courage to tackle his personal issues?

programme.title: Lifeline
programme.desc: Film ini berkisah tentang seorang pemadam kebakaran yang rela menerjang bahaya dan mempertaruhkan nyawanya demi menyelamatkan orang lain. Akan tetapi, apakah ia memiliki keberanian untuk menghadapi masalah pribadinya?

programme.title: Wolf Pack
programme.desc: The Wolf Pack squad led by Lao Diao, is a foreign-based team that specializes in overseas security jobs. In one of the missions, the squad discovers that a terrorist force is planning to destroy the country’s energy source. Lao Diao is now entrusted with the task of leading his squad to fight back. Can the Wolf Pack save the day?

programme.title: Hong Kong Family
programme.desc: Eight years ago, the family in a Hakka-walled village was torn apart during a combative winter solstice dinner. Eight years later, their cousin returns home from England and seeks to reunite the family for another winter solstice dinner. While things seem to be falling apart, this dinner may well be an opportunity to mend relations.

programme.title: Hong Kong Family
programme.desc: Eight years ago, the family in a Hakka-walled village was torn apart during a combative winter solstice dinner. Eight years later, their cousin returns home from England and seeks to reunite the family for another winter solstice dinner. programme.title: Where The Wind Blows
programme.desc: Detektif Lui Lok dan Nam Kong membangun sebuah sistem korupsi yang menimbulkan konflik antara anggota geng dan kepolisian. Kekuasaan keduanya pun berakhir saat ICAC melakukan pengejaran terhadap mereka.

programme.title: Where The Wind Blows
programme.desc: Detectives Lui Lok and Nam Kong build a corruption system that creates conflicts between the triad and the police. When ICAC hunts down the two, their control finally comes to an end.

programme.title: The Infernal Walker
programme.desc: Ting is an undercover police who infiltrates a triad and Tuen is a triad mole being planted into the police force. While Tang is tired of being an undercover cop, Tuen wishes to quit the triad and become a real police. When the triad boss sets a trap to uncover the moles' identity, the two must fight for themselves.

programme.title: Band Four
programme.desc: Seorang vokalis dari band indi bernama Band Four bertemu kembali dengan ayahnya yang seorang gitaris usai sepeninggalan sang ibu. Keduanya pun saling mendukung melalui kecintaan dan kegemaran mereka terhadap musik.

programme.title: Band Four
programme.desc: An aspiring singer of an indie band called Band Four reunites with her estranged guitarist father following the death of her mother. Together, they support each other through their love and passion for music.

programme.title: My Kung Fu Sweetheart
programme.desc: Phoenix’s (Cecilia Cheung) parents are martial arts superheroes, who hide their true identities while ferreting out evil martial artists. Phoenix gets the go-ahead to train in the misty mountains, where she learns of her all-important romantic destiny...

programme.title: The Way We Are
programme.desc: Set in Tin Shui Wai, a marginalised satellite town, Kwai is a middle-aged widow who works hard in a neighbourhood supermarket to support herself and her son. They lead a mundane but fulfilling life. When an elderly woman who lives alone moved in to Tin Shui Wai, Kwai strikes up a friendship with her and helps her ease into a new life.

programme.title: Caught In Time
programme.desc: Based on true events, Detective Zhong Cheng leads a task force in pursuit of Eagle, a criminal gang led by Zhang Sun. Highly methodical and disciplined, the gang manages to avoid capture after each heist. A decade later, the need to stop Eagle is more urgent than ever when Zhong Cheng realizes that his time is almost up to solve the case.

programme.title: A Guilty Conscience
programme.desc: Due to the negligence of sharp-tongued barrister Adrian, his innocent client is convicted of murder and sentenced to 17 years in jail. An opportunity to appeal the case and free his client arises a few years later, but in order to right his wrong, he must fight against one of the most powerful families in Hong Kong for justice to prevail.

programme.title: Chasing The Dragon
programme.desc: Ho datang ke Hong Kong sebagai imigran gelap pada tahun 1963 dan membangun kerajaan di dunia rahasia para pengedar narkoba dan polisi korup yang memerintah kota di bawah kekuasaan detektif terkenal bernama Lee Rock.

programme.title: Chasing The Dragon
programme.desc: Crippled Ho came to Hong Kong as an illegal immigrant in 1963 and ruthlessly carved an empire from the chaotic underworld of drug dealers and corrupt police that ruled the city under notorious detective Lee Rock.

programme.title: Life Must Go On
programme.desc: Saat program 'gimnasium tengah malam' untuk para siswi yang bermasalah menghadapi krisis pendanaan, pekerja sosial Yanki membentuk sebuah tim dodgeball untuk ikut dalam pertandingan guna menyelamatkan program tersebut.

programme.title: Life Must Go On
programme.desc: When the 'midnight gymnasium' programme for wayward teenage girls is at funding risk, social worker Yanki puts together a dodgeball team to compete in a match and save it.

programme.title: Kiko
programme.desc: Kiko tells of a child of a goldfish who is very independent, even though he is an only child. Kiko who is always cheerful has four good friends, namely Lola the discus fish, Ting Ting the crab, Patino the catfish and Poli the betta fish. On the other hand, the antagonists, Karkus the catfish and Pupus the eel, always make Kiko's life chaotic. One day, the lake where Kiko lives is polluted due to the reckless acts of humans, causing Kiko and friends to turn into mutants.

programme.title: Kiko
programme.desc: Kiko, seekor anak ikan mas koki yang sangat mandiri, walaupun ia anak tunggal. Kiko selalu riang dan memiliki empat sahabat baik yaitu Lola si ikan diskus, Ting Ting si kepiting, Patino si ikan patin dan Poli si ikan cupang. Di sisi lain, sosok antagonis, Karkus si ikan lele dan Pupus si belut, selalu membuat ricuh kehidupan Kiko.

programme.title: The World Of The Married
programme.desc: Ji Sun-woo adalah seorang dokter keluarga. Dia menikah dengan Lee Tae-oh. Keduanya telah memiliki seorang putra bernama Lee Joon-yeong. Keluarga ini tampak sempurna, memiliki segalanya, termasuk karier yang sukses dan keluarga yang bahagia. Tetapi ternyata, Sun-woo malah dikhianati oleh suaminya sendiri. Sementara sang suami, Tae-oh bermimpi menjadi sutradara film terkenal. Dia menjalankan bisnis hiburan dengan dukungan dan sokongan ekonomi dari istrinya. Sebenarnya Tae-oh mencintai sang istri, tapi ia malah jatuh pada hubungan berbahaya. Di sisi lain, Sun-woo merencanakan balas dendam terhadap suaminya.

programme.title: TOP Masih Ngojek
programme.desc: Cerita berfokus pada kehidupan Sutisna (diperankan oleh Andri Sulistiandri) dan Ojak (diperankan oleh Eza Yayang), dua tukang ojek yang menghadapi berbagai tantangan dalam kehidupan sehari-hari. Mereka berjuang untuk mencari nafkah, menjaga hubungan dengan keluarga, dan membantu sesama di lingkungan mereka.

programme.title: Cat & Keet
programme.desc: Cat and Keet embark on an journey filled with hysterical escapades. Colourful characters like Sethji, Katreena, the neighbouring cat, and the 'Mean Cats' street gang who make appearances and promise to make one laugh ones guts out.

programme.title: Doo Bee Doo
programme.desc: Kisah berpusat pada tiga sahabat Ariel, Bias dan Cody yang tanpa sengaja menemukan seorang bayi perempuan bernama Sheyna di dalam taksi bersama belanjaan Ariel. Upaya mereka untuk mengembalikan bayi tersebut gagal, sehingga mereka memutuskan untuk membawa Sheyna ke kosan mereka. Namun, kosan tersebut melarang penghuni membawa hewan peliharaan atau anak-anak, memaksa mereka menyembunyikan keberadaan Sheyna dari pemilik kos.​

programme.title: Terbelenggu Rindu (Vision Prime)
programme.desc: A story about Amira, a beautiful, kind-hearted woman who always saw life in a positive light. Her life was going smoothly until the death of her husband and daughter, along with a series of relentless hardships, left her struggling to move forward.

programme.title: Terbelenggu Rindu (Vision Prime)
programme.desc: Cerita tentang Amira perempuan cantik, baik hati, dan selalu positif dalam memandang hidup. Kehidupannya berjalan baik-baik saja namun setelah kematian suami dan putrinya serta masalah yang datang bertubi-tubi membuatnya menjadi semakin terpuruk untuk melanjutkan hidupnya.

programme.title: Ikatan Cinta
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang dua bersaudara, Andin (kakak) dan Elsa (adik). Tanpa mereka sadari mencintai pria yang sama, Nino. Hubungan mereka yang buruk menjadi lebih buruk ketika Elsa tahu bahwa Nino akan menikahi Andin. Pernikahan Nino dan Andin mendapat dukungan sang ayah, namun ditentang oleh sang ibu.

programme.title: Kau Ditakdirkan Untukku
programme.desc: The story of Alya, a tough and independent girl who gets into a contract marriage with Devan, a wealthy man. Over time, the relationship that started as a pretense slowly turns into a genuine feeling of love. But their journey is not as easy as imagined.

programme.title: Kau Ditakdirkan Untukku
programme.desc: Cerita tentang Alya, seorang gadis tangguh dan mandiri yang terlibat pernikahan kontrak dengan Devan, seorang pria kaya raya. Seiring waktu, hubungan yang semula hanya pura-pura perlahan berubah menjadi perasaan cinta yang tulus. Namun perjalanan mereka tidak semudah yang dibayangkan.

programme.title: New Top Files
programme.desc: Top Files merupakan sebuah program acara televisi magazine yang ditayangkan di Stasiun Televisi iNews

programme.title: Tamu Tak Diundang
programme.desc: Ibu Aminah seorang wanita yang berumur 52 tahun gelisah karena sebentar lagi akan memasuki masa menopause. Namun tidak disangka, dokter malah menyatakan Bu Aminah hamil lagi.

programme.title: Mantan IPA & IPS
programme.desc: Setelah lulus dari SMU Garuda, Rifki dan teman-temannya dari jurusan IPA dan IPS melanjutkan studi ke Universitas Harapan Bangsa. Mereka berusaha memulai lembaran baru dalam kehidupan kampus. Namun, konflik lama antara anak IPA dan IPS masih membekas, menciptakan ketegangan di antara mereka.​

programme.title: Gober Parijs Van Java (Vision Prime)
programme.desc: Gober Parijs Van Java mengangkat kisah tiga pengemudi ojek online (Gober) di Bandung. Drama ini menyajikan campuran nuansa romansa, komedi, dan perjuangan hidup yang dekat dengan keseharian banyak orang.

programme.title: OMG
programme.desc: Program yang mengangkat permasalahan sosial yang terjadi di kehidupan sehari-hari dan sering melibatkan perempuan. OMG!! dikemas secara ringan dan informatif.

programme.title: Mencintaimu Sekali Lagi
programme.desc: Arini, seorang wanita karir yang cantik. Ia adalah seorang Makeup Artist yang sangat terkenal, tapi sayangnya dibalik karirnya yang cemerlang ia memiliki kisah percintaan yang tidak begitu mulus.
